# Project Structure

## Directory Structure
```
src/
├── routes/     # SvelteKit routes and pages
├── lib/        # Shared components, utilities, and types
│   ├── components/
│   ├── utils/
│   └── types/
├── app.html    # Main HTML template
├── app.css     # Global styles
└── app.d.ts    # TypeScript declarations

e2e/           # End-to-end tests
static/        # Static assets
```

## Key Dependencies

### Core
- SvelteKit v2.16.0
- Svelte v5.0.0
- TypeScript v5.0.0
- Vite v6.2.6

### Styling
- Tailwind CSS v4.0.0
- @tailwindcss/forms v0.5.9
- @tailwindcss/typography v0.5.15

### Testing
- Vitest v3.0.0
- Playwright v1.49.1
- @testing-library/svelte v5.2.4
- @testing-library/jest-dom v6.6.3

### Code Quality
- ESLint v9.18.0
- Prettier v3.4.2
- prettier-plugin-svelte v3.3.3
- prettier-plugin-tailwindcss v0.6.11

## Configuration Files
- `svelte.config.js` - SvelteKit configuration
- `vite.config.ts` - Vite configuration
- `tsconfig.json` - TypeScript configuration
- `playwright.config.ts` - E2E test configuration
- `vitest.config.ts` - Unit test configuration
- `.prettierrc` - Prettier rules
- `eslint.config.js` - ESLint configuration

## Development Commands
```bash
# Development
npm run dev          # Start dev server
npm run check        # Type checking
npm run check:watch  # Watch types
npm run format       # Format code
npm run lint         # Lint code

# Testing
npm run test:unit    # Unit tests
npm run test:e2e     # E2E tests
npm run test         # All tests

# Build
npm run build        # Production build
npm run preview      # Preview build
```
